  <TITLE>Feature attribute is not working for razor page</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>### Describe the bug Feature attribute is not applied to razor page. Razor pages are always tied to the module. ### To Reproduce 1. Create a Module with a feature 2. Add a Razor Page 3. Add Feature attribute to razor page 4. Enable the module and the feature, it will serve Razor page 5. Disable Feature - notice that Razor page is still served. ### Expected behavior When feature is disabled it should not serve the Razor Page.</DESCRIPTION>
